T1  - Mechanisation, employment and productivity in Sudanese agriculture
AU  - Disney, Richard
AU  - Elbashir, A.A.
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 16
IS  - 3
SP  - 249
EP  - 262
PY  - 1984
DA  - 1984/12/01/
